high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter next to the stove.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Set down the knife on the counter in front of the sink.
Pick up a tomato slice from the tomato in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the table.
Put the tomato slice in the bowl next to the wall on the table.
Pick up the bowl with the tomato slice from the table.
Turn right and walk to the microwave.
Put the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a tomato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn to the right to face the sink.
Cut the tomato in the sink into slices.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up the tomato slice out of the sink.
Turn right and walk forward to face the kitchen table.
Place the tomato slice in the bowl on the back of the kitchen table.
Pick up the bowl with the tomato slice in it on the back of the kitchen table.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Place the bowl with the tomato slice in it in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a tomato slice in it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the knife to the right of the stove.
Turn around and head towards the sink on your left.
Cut the tomato in the sink into slices.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn right, walk to the counter and then turn right towards the round table.
Place the slice of tomato on the plate closest to the chair.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Turn right towards the microwave.
Place the plate with the tomato into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the plate with a slice of tomato into the microwave.
